formatDescription: JT (Jupiter Tessellation) is an openly-published ISO-standardised (ISO 14306:2012, ISO/DIS 14306 V2, ISO 14306:2017) 3D CAD data exchange format used for product visualisation, collaboration, digital mockups, and other purposes. It was developed by Siemens.
